== Homing Sequence ==

"Test" -> "ArcusAdapter" : **CALL** home()
"Test" -> "ArcusAdapter" : **WAIT** wait_until_stopped()
"ArcusAdapter" --> "Test" : **RETURN** Position: Position2D(x=-50.9684, y=0.7412)

== Move to 200mm ==

"Test" -> "ArcusAdapter" : **CALL** move_to(Position2D(x=200.0, y=200.0))
"Test" -> "ArcusAdapter" : **WAIT** wait_until_stopped()
"ArcusAdapter" --> "Test" : **RETURN** Position: Position2D(x=199.9932, y=199.9932)

== Return to Home ==

